msgstr "Solar limpio que la península se ha visto obligada a malgastar"

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:24
msgid "What we threw away that day"
msgstr "Lo que tiramos ese día"

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:29
msgid ""
"The sun did its job; the system didn’t. Clean MWh left sitting on the "
"wires."
msgstr ""
"El sol cumplió; el sistema no. MWh limpios quedándose en los cables."

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:33
msgid "Rough euros down the drain"
msgstr "Euros tirados (aprox.)"

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:38
msgid ""
"Ballpark only: your site’s €/MWh × those MWh—not your bill, not a market "
"truth, still galling."
msgstr ""
"Orden de magnitud: tu €/MWh del sitio × esos MWh—no es tu factura ni la "
"verdad del mercado; igual indigna."

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:44
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    About %(eur_h)s each hour on average—%(mwh_h)s—and it stacks up "
"faster than it should.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Unos %(eur_h)s cada hora de media—%(mwh_h)s—y se acumula más rápido "
"de lo que debería.\n"
"    "

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:50
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    About %(mwh_h)s each hour on average—quietly, relentlessly, all day.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Unos %(mwh_h)s cada hora de media, en silencio, sin tregua, todo el "
"día.\n"
"    "

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:56
msgid "Year to date—still counting:"
msgstr "Lo que llevamos de año—y seguimos sumando:"

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:62
msgid "at that illustrative €/MWh—too much to treat as noise."
msgstr "a ese €/MWh ilustrativo—demasiado para tomarlo como ruido."

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:68
msgid "MWh—and the calendar still has pages left."
msgstr "MWh—y al calendario aún le quedan hojas."

